title: Allen Beats Mahomes, How Good Is NY Football??
description:
Welcome back to (debatable) with hosts Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth featuring Bill Barnwell and Spencer Hall! On today’s show: What was your reaction to Josh Allen and the Bills beating Patrick Mahomes and the Chiefs? How good are the Giants and the Jets? What does Tennessee's win over Alabama mean for both teams? Plus, a breakdown of struggling NFL teams such as the Bucs, Packers, Cardinals, and Ravens!
